title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 1PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 1PM” game were:
7-0-1-4
(seven, zero, one, four)
